oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Collection of relics
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Collection of relics including: harmonica parts, a ring, minie balls, a toe tap from a shoe, a buckle from suspenders, portions of belt buckles, a hook, a portion of a fork, a corkscrew, buttons from a sword belt, a bayonet scabbard tip, a Maynard cartridge casing, and other assorted items.
